          <div class="post single" id="post-415">
            <h1><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110401101355/http://www.miptalk.com/thomas-steitz/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Thomas Steitz – A Nobel Profession">Thomas Steitz &#8211; A Nobel Profession</a></h1>
            <div class="info">
	         		<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110401101355/http://www.miptalk.com/category/science/" title="Science" class="first">Science</a>|
              <span>3.13.10</span>|
	         		<a href="#comment">No Comments</a>
            </div>
                        <p style="text-align: center;"><img title="Thomas Steitz" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20110401101355im_/http://www.miptalk.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/Thomas-Steitz.jpg" alt="Thomas Steitz" width="467" height="264"/></p>
<!-- Begin: podPress -->
<div class="podPress_content">
